title: Catalan independence movement stages mass protest in Barcelona
description:
Thousands of pro-independence Catalans take part in a rally against the trial of 12 of the movement's leaders. As our correspondent in Barcelona, Kusai Kedri reports, the march comes at a time of heightened tensions in Spain on the eve of a snap national election.
